    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公告：11 bit studios和Dead Mage由此获得的收益将100%捐给国际人道协会(<strong>Humane World for Animals</strong>)慈善组织。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Children of Morta: Paws and Claws》自发布以来已共计为需要救助的动物们筹集到超过460000$的善款。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1317160/extras/138d1f50d517cf8567693ff7b19f5b2f.poster.avif?t=1748861419\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1317160/extras/138d1f50d517cf8567693ff7b19f5b2f.webm?t=1748861419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1317160/extras/138d1f50d517cf8567693ff7b19f5b2f.mp4?t=1748861419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们是夜间的猎手，白天的动物。它们会嚎叫、咆哮、发出嘶嘶声和喃喃声——但最重要的是，它们会和我们一样感觉和思考。它们的生命也和我们的一样珍贵。本DLC为游戏增加了几种新内容，比如动物避难所系统，新的加成、动画和事件。但还远不仅如此。本DLC还将帮到那些急需救助的动物——不是在虚拟的游戏中，而是现实中真实的动物。<strong>11 bit studios和Dead Mage从Humane World for Animals（《尖牙利爪》）DLC获得的收益将100%捐给国际人道协会慈善组织</strong>。该组织致力于为全世界范围内的动物提供援助。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1317160/extras/fc905709becace7daf9c31533726138d.poster.avif?t=1748861419\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1317160/extras/fc905709becace7daf9c31533726138d.webm?t=1748861419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1317160/extras/fc905709becace7daf9c31533726138d.mp4?t=1748861419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《尖牙利爪》DLC主要新特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>动物避难所系统</strong>将为家中增加一块全新区域！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 一群多种多样的动物将来家中拜访：有鹿、狐狸、鸟儿等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>新机制</strong>：使用零食喂养并照顾动物们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 为柏格森家族新增和动物相关的<strong>加成</strong>（经验值获取、移动速度等等）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 新家族互动事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 超过100种大大小小的新动画，为你展现新动物朋友们的生活百态！</p>",
